      <p>Links worth reading, frequent news, and answers to your questions at <%= link_to "@themanual", "https://twitter.com/themanual" %>.</p>
      <p><a class="twitter-follow-button" href="https://twitter.com/themanual" data-show-count="true" data-size="large" data-lang="en">Follow @themanual</a></p>
